{"tid":770740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上環My Central首現撻大定 長實沒收200萬","createTime":"2018-08-07T10:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T03:00:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f469f1434799148aa1c96663faa5f954ba6e17","tid":770740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T10:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180807/large/1533635924_ec9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180807%2Flarge%2F1533635924_ec9e.jpg&h=a44e173d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長實地產（1113）與市建局合作的上環嘉咸街My Central，剛錄得首宗撻大定個案。土地註冊處資料顯示，15樓C室，實用面積674方呎，兩房間隔，去年11月原以2,000.5萬元售出，呎價29,681元，本月2日已終止買賣合約，買家是次撻定料被發展商沒收10%定金，損失200萬元。"},{"pid":"1b487e77bd69c203d98885c7681a14548ad00658","tid":770740,"uid":41508,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cadc73f9abf0f61436b5aca4ee2823acc5171c0","tid":770740,"uid":183302,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"樓下就豬肉檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  高級極有限喇"},{"pid":"0b795a4add2d0ab79860f140b10330640ad6c020","tid":770740,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"錢真多"},{"pid":"3d2776037092bb9dabbf87eb44542a4cf5afc03e","tid":770740,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:08:38.000Z","msg":"街鋪fatfat"},{"pid":"cdeeeb5b181fdb8291d038fdc98e97e2114b2a00","tid":770740,"uid":8439,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1cadc73f9abf0f61436b5aca4ee2823acc5171c0","tid":770740,"uid":183302,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"樓下就豬肉檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  高級極有限喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"個名高檔咪得"},{"p